OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FUTV's former Political Editor was
OL,7,Fremembered by MLAs on Monday during
OL,8,Fthe day's Assembly sitting.
OL,10,FKen Reid spent nearly thirty years
OL,11,Fworking for the broadcaster where he
OL,12,Freported on many of the worst
OL,13,Fatrocities of the Troubles before
OL,14,Fgoing on to chronicle the peace
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,17,FHe died last Wednesday following an
OL,18,Fillness.
