OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FThe Speaker of the Assembly, Edwin
OL,7,FPoots, had known Ken for years, and
OL,8,Fsaid: "Ken and I disagreed on many
OL,9,Fthings; Linfield, Cliftonville,
OL,10,FLiverpool, Everton, Van Morrison. His
OL,11,Ffootball taste was terrible, his music
OL,12,Ftaste was terrible, but regardless he
OL,13,Fwas a really fine gentleman and
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland is the poorer for the
OL,15,Fpassing of Ken Reid."
OL,17,FA heartfelt tribute was also made by
OL,18,Fthe Health Minister, Mike Nesbitt, who
OL,19,Fhad worked with Ken for many years at
OL,20,FUTV.
