OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FHe said: "He was for that time my
OL,7,Fbroadcasting brother and for that I am
OL,8,Ftruly grateful. I hope you know
OL,9,Fyourself, you are loved and you are
OL,10,Fmissed."
OL,12,FKen's funeral will take place in his
OL,13,Fadopted home town of Ballymena on
OL,14,FThursday 28 November.
